---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import BackAndForthSection from '../components/BackAndForthSection.astro';

const title = 'Benefits | Window Film Philadelphia | Leading Window Film Solutions';
const description = 'Window Film Philadelphia is honored to provide an extensive scope of window film benefits for your home or business. Get your free quote!';
import CTAStrip from './../components/CTAStrip.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} canonical='https://www.windowfilmphiladelphia.net/benefits/'>
  <section class="page-hero" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(40,40,40,0.62), rgba(40,40,40,0.80)), url('/images/2021-08-philadelphia-window-film-glare-privacy.jpg'); background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Window Film Benefits for Philadelphia</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Window Film Benefits for Philadelphia'}
  body={'From energy savings and comfort to privacy, security, and aesthetic appeal, window film offers a variety of benefits for Philadelphia homes and businesses. Window film delivers an incredible money-saving solution to address a wide variety of needs across any industry. With the most effective products available on the market, we’re happy to help you achieve your project goals and create better function, comfort, and productivity.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-08-philadelphia-window-film-glare-privacy.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'philadelphia-window-film-glare-privacy'}
  flip={false}
  altBg={false}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Privacy'}
  body={'With window tint, you can get the privacy you need to keep your affairs and activities confidential. Window tint provides a modern day solution for adding privacy to your home or office without blocking out light or reducing the level of brightness. It’s perfect for conference rooms, waiting areas, patient or tenant rooms, and even your home windows. At Window Film Philadelphia, we carry a number of privacy window films that are excellent for both commercial and residential use. Explore beautiful styles from industry leading manufacturers like Solyx, 3M, LLumar, and more.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-08-philadelphia-window-film-glare-reduction.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'philadelphia-window-film-glare-reduction'}
  flip={true}
  altBg={true}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Glare Reduction'}
  body={'Glare is a common issue for many high rise buildings in Philadelphia and properties along Lake Michigan. It can be difficult to work on your computer or watch tv when too much glare is present. Window tint provides a solution that can help reduce the amount of glare in your home or office and improve your screen viewing comfort, allowing you to keep better focus and work more productively. While other options like blinds and shade screens block out light, glare reducing window tint does not. These window films single out the types of light that create glare and reject only these select frequencies. Natural light passes through with ease, keeping the room bright and beautiful.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-08-philadelphia-window-film-energy-savings.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'philadelphia-window-film-energy-savings'}
  flip={false}
  altBg={false}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Energy Savings'}
  body={'Window tint offers an easy solution for optimizing the energy efficiency and comfort of your building. Window film boosts the glazing performance of your windows so you don’t have to worry about high energy costs during the summer or winter. It’s a great way to reduce your carbon footprint and save money on your monthly utility costs. At Window Film Philadelphia, we carry both clear and tinted energy efficient window films. Choose a reflective or tinted option to give your exterior a subtle look or opt for a completely clear film to keep your windows as they are.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-08-philadelphia-window-film-uv-protection.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'philadelphia-window-film-uv-protection'}
  flip={true}
  altBg={true}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'UV Protection'}
  body={'Being exposed to too much sunlight can cause your furniture and flooring to look worn and faded. Window tint blocks out 99.9% of uv rays that cause fading and heat damage, keeping your space looking beautiful and vibrant throughout the years and is also a smart way to protect your health. Window tint provides uv protection equivalent to SPF 1000 and can help prevent skin and eye disease. Families can feel more at ease knowing that they don’t have to worry about being exposed to ultraviolet radiation. And employers can offer a healthier work environment and gain the trust and loyalty of their staff.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-08-philadelphia-window-film-anti-graffiti-window-film-scratches-film.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'philadelphia-window-film-anti-graffiti-window-film-scratches-film'}
  flip={false}
  altBg={false}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Anti Graffiti'}
  body={'If you live or work in an older neighborhood or an inner city area of Philadelphia, you may have experienced issues with graffiti. Graffiti is extremely common in big cities, and Philadelphia is no exception. Window film offers a solution that can help keep transit systems, schools, and commercial properties graffiti free and save money! Durable graffiti protective films are easily applied to high risk areas to prevent vandalism-related damage. Window Film Philadelphia is proud to offer the most advanced anti-graffiti and sacrificial films on the market. We work with innovative manufacturers like 3M, Graffiti Shield, and LLumar to provide our customers with top of the line solutions for deterring vandalism on glass, metal, and mirror surfaces.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-08-philadelphia-hd-clear-conference-room-window-film.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'philadelphia-window-film-anti-graffiti-window-film-scratches-film'}
  flip={true}
  altBg={true}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Decorative & Promotional'}
  body={'With window film, you can easily enhance the aesthetic appearance of your home, office, or commercial property. Window film offers an elegant and stylish way to add color and privacy to windows and glass partitions and is a much more economical alternative to designer glass. Have your film printed with your business name, logo, or pattern of your choice for a unique, personalized appearance. Or go all out with a custom building wrap that revives and modernizes your exterior! Home and business owners can’t go wrong with our modern, stylish decorative film options. Choose from beautiful patterns, prints, and graphics, as well as elegant etched and frosted styles to give your space the perfect, curated look.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/2021-08-philadelphia-window-film-ballistic-resistant-window-film.jpg'}
  imageAlt={'philadelphia-window-film-ballistic-resistant-window-film'}
  flip={false}
  altBg={false}
/>

  <BackAndForthSection
  heading={'Ballistic Resistance'}
  body={'Life in the city can be dangerous and not everyone has the best of intentions. Ballistic resistant window film systems offer Philadelphia schools, government buildings, and commercial properties an advanced method of security. These durable window film systems can deter everything from intruders to gunfire and explosions and are a smart choice for buildings of all types. For schools, government offices, airports, and museums, they’re truly a worthwhile investment and a more affordable alternative to bulletproof glass. Window Film Philadelphia partners with industry leaders like C-Bond and 3M to give our customers access to the best ballistic resistant window systems available on the market today.'}
  imageSrc={'/images/bomb-proof-window-film-Philadephia.jpeg'}
  imageAlt={''}
  flip={true}
  altBg={true}
/>

  <CTAStrip />
</BaseLayout>
